The study is an intervention, Phase II COPCORD study.

 (COPCORD= Community Oriented Program to Control Rheumatic Diseases).

 The purpose of this study is to find if Back School training has any benefit on low back pain of the workers in a pharmaceutical factory in Tehran suburbs.

